    {
      "description": "The only primitive token carrying Sunshine (#faa31b) is scoped/named as a CTA-fallback-specific entity (background_gradient_cta_fallback) though its key (color.primary.sunshine) implies general primary-color status. Sunshine is used broadly (chart emphasis, wave colorway, campaign headline colorway, masthead gradient stop) — no generic Sunshine primary token exists, causing an ID/key mismatch and functional omission.",
      "finding_id": "f_lisraya_004",
      "finding_type": "wrong_typing",
      "proposed_patch": {
        "entity_kind": "token_primitive",
        "op": "add",
        "payload": {
          "default": "#faa31b",
          "key": "color.primary.sunshine",
          "note": "rename/generalize; retain cta-fallback usage as a reference"
